I keep getting an error code '2350' when installing. Can anybody help please?!

It is usual for antivirus makers to have their heuristics  recognize characteristic keygen code and label it falsely as a virus, for the benefit of vendors. Often, just using the word "keygen" in any filename, regardless of its nature, triggers a false positive. Don't be fooled by this tactic-- it is a false-alarm feature included in antivirus software SOLELY to combat posting of shared (warez) programs....
